                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4337" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0681</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8730 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">说走就走的旅游者——传统旅行社何去何从？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tourists Who Just Walk Away——Where Do Traditional Travel Agencies Go?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王海弘，马宁，杨玉帆，何文俊，王颖，孙雨桐，孙明霞，陈琼玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">辽宁大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京青年旅行社股份有限公司大连分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">互联网+；传统旅行社；管理模式创新 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internet +, Traditional travel agency, Innovation of management mode </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018 年，在互联网大潮下，旅游者的思维方式和行为方式发生了巨大的 变化，对旅游产品的质量要求以及便利度要求也随之上升。其中，火爆的线上旅 行业务也吸引了相关各方纷纷进入，这给传统旅行社带来了挑战。本案例以北京 青年旅行社股份有限公司大连分公司的创建与发展为场景，通过分析服务质量差 距模型、改进旅行社宣传策略、落实旅行社电子商务发展策略，对症下药提高旅 行社服务质量，从而提高旅行者满意度，留住说走就走的旅游者，寻找到新时代 传统旅行社的创新发展模式。通过对本案例的阅读与分析，在了解传统旅行社经 营模式的基础上，引导学生学习如何进行管理创新，掌握传统旅行社提高市场竞 争力的关键要素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2018, under the tide of the Internet, the way of thinking and behavior of tourists have undergone great changes, and the quality and convenience requirements of tourism products have also increased. Among them, the hot online travel business has also attracted relevant parties to enter, which brings challenges to traditional travel agencies. This case by the Beijing youth travel service co., LTD., Dalian branch for the creation and development scenarios, by building a connection platform, workers and tourists to achieve internal and external satisfaction has increased, so as to retain said visitors come away and traditional travel agencies to find new era of innovation and development mode. Based on the reading and analysis of this case, students are guided to learn how to make management innovation and master the key elements of improving market competitiveness of traditional travel agencies on the basis of understanding the business model of traditional travel agencies. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅行社经营与管理》、《旅游电子商务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">旅行社的产品开发 旅行社的质量管理 旅行社的信息化管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-01</td>
                            </tr>
